{"tid":1699848,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共欲將佛滅盡  雕刻11年29米釋迦牟尼山體雕像遭炸毀　","createTime":"2019-11-08T08:02:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T08:16:56.000Z","uid":141060,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d906157321867affcc9cad583b1da92e5b1c1c91","tid":1699848,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T08:02:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://zh.bitterwinter.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/%E9%87%8A%E8%BF%A6%E7%89%9F%E5%B0%BC%E7%9F%B3%E9%9B%95%E5%88%BB%E8%A2%AB%E7%82%B8%E6%AF%81%E5%89%8D%E5%90%8E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.bitterwinter.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F%25E9%2587%258A%25E8%25BF%25A6%25E7%2589%259F%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E7%259F%25B3%25E9%259B%2595%25E5%2588%25BB%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%2582%25B8%25E6%25AF%2581%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%2590%258E.jpg&h=706cfcac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全國範圍露天宗教造像不斷遭摧毀，當地負責的官員被威脅，違背中央拆佛像命令者將被停職。<br />\n6月中旬，吉林省吉林市豐滿區一座29米高的釋迦牟尼山體雕像被政府以「超高」為由炸毀，施工期間政府人員在現場監督。<br />\n<br />\n據知情人透露，這座佛祖山體雕像由私人出資約300萬元人民幣（約42萬美元）建造，歷經11年雕刻出佛像輪廓，還未打磨、鍍金，就被政府強行炸毀。<br />\n<br />\n炸毀佛像之前，出資者就遭到政府官員的警告稱拆除佛像是全國大局勢，誰也抵抗不了，如果他反對拆佛像，就把他抓捕關押。據政府內部人士透露，如果不拆石佛，當地官員都得被撤職。<br />\n<br />\n河南省洛陽孟津縣龍興寺內一座約10米高的露天釋迦牟尼佛像也被當地官員勒令拆除。據知情人透露，當地官員遭上級警告稱如果三天拆不掉，自動離職！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://zh.bitterwinter.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/%E4%BD%9B%E7%A5%96%E5%83%8F%E4%BB%8E%E8%A2%AB%E5%B0%81%E7%9B%96%E5%88%B0%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%86%E9%99%A4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.bitterwinter.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F%25E4%25BD%259B%25E7%25A5%2596%25E5%2583%258F%25E4%25BB%258E%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%25B0%2581%25E7%259B%2596%25E5%2588%25B0%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2586%25E9%2599%25A4.jpg&h=4c09fba6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n7月17至18日，在當地官員的命令下，工人連續作業拆除佛像。一名村幹部說：「中央下達命令，所有的露天佛像都得拆！中國誰有習近平的權力大！誰敢不聽！」<br />\n<br />\n據當地村民透露，為保佛像免遭拆除，該寺信徒曾用遮陽網將大佛像遮蓋，但還是難逃被拆。<br />\n<br />\n「沒處講理去，現在就和文化大革命一樣，就是推倒、毀掉一切與佛有關的東西。」一名信徒無奈地說，「共產黨怕人以後都信這個（佛），不信共產黨。將來（百姓）都有信仰，共產黨不完了麼，所以就趕緊下令全拆。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://zh.bitterwinter.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/%E5%88%BB%E7%9D%80%E4%BD%9B%E5%AD%97%E7%9A%84%E7%9F%B3%E7%A2%91%E8%A2%AB%E6%94%BE%E5%80%92%E5%89%8D%E5%90%8E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.bitterwinter.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F%25E5%2588%25BB%25E7%259D%2580%25E4%25BD%259B%25E5%25AD%2597%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%259F%25B3%25E7%25A2%2591%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%2580%2592%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%2590%258E.jpg&h=e81961fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不僅佛像被拆，甚至連刻在石碑上的「佛」字都不允許存在。今年春，吉林省白山市撫松縣露水河鎮一佛堂外刻著「佛」字的石碑被當地政府勒令清除，原因是「政府規定不准擺放露天宗教標識物」。最終，這座屹立了十多年的石碑被放倒。"},{"pid":"b456bd0c41fb6a64e9f0c070278730af8565898b","tid":1699848,"uid":15605,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T08:03:29.000Z","msg":"塔利班當年都做過，跟住就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"000f1f09365e8b56c32f2ecb6ecdaf9884c4bce2","tid":1699848,"uid":222966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T08:04:25.000Z","msg":"Source? 我要po俾我老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9915930becf28c1ffc837d8fa55dfa21e675856","tid":1699848,"uid":193217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"000f1f09365e8b56c32f2ecb6ecdaf9884c4bce2","tid":1699848,"uid":222966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T08:04:25.000Z","msg":"Source? 我要po俾我老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T08:05:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.bannednews.org/2019/11/blog-post_619.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bannednews.org%2F2019%2F11%2Fblog-post_619.html&d=6wykgBqlsxypO2QI0oCEUrCEdHrHTgyyxjjYSTVVVd4%3D&h=336f25c4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bannednews.org/2019/11/blog-post_619.html</a>"},{"pid":"1c129377e3a1d95dff562a2adab82cdc79759be8","tid":1699848,"